OS_ExitAndDie  (&50)
#Parent OS_
=>	R0 =	pointer to <error block=>swi_errorblock>
	R1 =	"ABEX" (&58454241) if return code
	R2 =	return code
	R3 =	pointer to module name

<=	Never returns

This SWI does exactly what <OS_Exit> does, but in addition it kills the module in R3.
#Line
See <PRM 1, page 318=>PRM-1:318>.
